## 10. Final Architecture

```
┌──────────┐     ┌──────────┐
│  Uploader │     │Downloader│
│  (Client) │     │ (Client) │
└────┬──────┘     └─────┬────┘
     │                   │
     │  presigned URLs   │  CDN signed URLs
     ▼                   ▼
┌─────────────────────────────┐
│   LB & API Gateway          │
└─────────────┬───────────────┘
              │
              ▼
┌─────────────────────────────┐
│      File Service            │  ← generates presigned URLs, manages metadata
└──────┬──────────────┬───────┘
       │              │
       ▼              ▼
┌────────────┐  ┌──────────┐
│ Metadata DB│  │    S3    │  ← actual file bytes
│ (DynamoDB) │  └────┬─────┘
└────────────┘       │
                     ▼
               ┌──────────┐
               │    CDN   │  ← cached at edge for fast downloads
               └──────────┘
```

**Component responsibilities:**

| Component | Role |
|-----------|------|
| File Service | Control plane — generates presigned URLs, manages metadata. Never touches file bytes. |
| Metadata DB (DynamoDB) | Stores file metadata, chunk status, SharedFiles table |
| S3 | Stores actual file bytes. Handles scaling, durability, multipart assembly. |
| CDN (CloudFront) | Caches files at edge locations for fast downloads worldwide |
| LB & API Gateway | Routing, SSL termination, rate limiting, request validation |

