## Quick Reference: Upload Decision Tree

```
User wants to upload a file
│
├─ File < 10MB?
│   └─ Single presigned URL PUT → done
│
├─ File 10MB - 50GB?
│   └─ Chunked multipart upload:
│       ├─ Calculate file + chunk fingerprints
│       ├─ Check for existing partial upload (resumability)
│       ├─ Get presigned URL per chunk
│       ├─ Upload chunks in parallel
│       ├─ Backend verifies each with ListParts
│       └─ CompleteMultipartUpload → assembled
│
└─ Compress first?
    ├─ Text/CSV/logs → Yes (Zstandard)
    ├─ Images/video → No (already compressed)
    └─ Encrypting after? → Always compress BEFORE encrypt
```

